<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c1">" وِبحَلْوَنَة في سَلْوَنَة * سَاقُواْ الهَبَلْ عَالشَّيْطَنَة "</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
